md:
giải nghĩa từ "stanley" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ tương tự.

* Stanley (noun)
	+ Meaning: A person who is strong and brave.
	+ Example: "He's a real Stanley, always ready to defend his friends."
	+ Related words: brave, strong, courageous
	+ Synonyms: hero, champion, warrior

* Stanley (proper noun)
	+ Meaning: A name of a person, place, or thing.
	+ Example: "Stanley Kubrick was a famous film director."
	+ Related words: name, person, place
	+ Synonyms: title, label, designation

Note: The meaning of "Stanley" can vary depending on the context in which it is used. The above definitions are just a few examples of how the word can be used.
